				<td colspan="2"><span>Swarming pre 50ish was always hard for me too. One thing to make sure of is that when you get your initial pull make sure you dont do any damage to any of the mobs. Just get proximity agro and the charmd mob should take on most if not all of the mobs. Even when i was higher lvl i still got one or 2 mobs to chase me and like 2 on my charmed mob. Hope that helps = )</span></td>
