				<td><img src="/skins/default/images/user_IsOffline.gif" alt="Polara is not online. Last active: 3/6/2005 3:53:00 AM" border="0" />&nbsp;<a class="SmallBoldText" href="/User/UserProfile.aspx?UserName=Polara">Polara</a><br></td>
