				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Swarming - Do I just not understand it?<a name="70921"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Dec 11 04 11:36 PM</span></td>
