				<td><img src="/skins/default/images/user_IsOffline.gif" alt="Hilbur is not online. Last active: 3/8/2005 11:59:11 AM" border="0" />&nbsp;<a class="SmallBoldText" href="/User/UserProfile.aspx?UserName=Hilbur">Hilbur</a><br></td>
