This is an oft-repeated statement that's just plain wrong.  If you were a bard when they changed the 39 song from a 3-tick song to a 1-minute song, you would have seen the screams of &quot;NERF!&quot;  &quot;THEY ARE TRYING TO KILL SWARM KITING!&quot;
<br />

<br />
Swarming can easily be done with a 3-tick song, arguably in some ways that are even easier than the one-minute song.  Plus, with the 27 song you can do it all night long, whereas with the 39 song you are mana-regen limited.
